The following technologies are involved in the application:Spring Boot, JUnit, Maven, Postgreasql, Mockito.
1.Creat client(POST)
Exemple of json request

{"firstName": "name",
"lastName": "lastname",
"birthday": "1993-03-03",
"gender": "MALE",
"phoneNumbers": [{"phoneNumber": "123321414"}]}

2.Endpoint to create call(POST)
  Exemple:
  
{
  "callersPhoneNumber": {
    "phoneNumber": "323214414212"
  },
  "recipientsPhoneNumber": {
    "phoneNumber": "380951234567"
  },
  "date": "2019-06-07 10:10:10",
  "duration": 1231,
  "city": "Dnipro"
}

3. Endpoint to get information about number of calls per each city (GET)
   http://localhost:8080/calls

4. Endpoint for providing information about the longest call for defined client id and specified date range.(GET)
http://localhost:8080/calls/{clientId}/longest_call?start={starDate}end={endDate}
